(thirdQuint)Marijuana for Cancer Pain.

 To take part in this study, you must have ongoing cancer pain which is currently being treated with opioids.

 If you meet all the eligibility criteria you will be admitted to the General Clinical Research Center at San Francisco General Hospital for 9 days.

 The treatment consists of smoking one marijuana cigarette 3 times a day.

