 Marijuana for Cancer Pain@highlight

To find out if it is safe and effective to use smoked marijuana in combination with opioids to treat cancer pain.

 The study will evaluate whether smoked marijuana, when used with opioids, will have an effect on pain relief, and to see if marijuana reduces the side effects of opioids, which include nausea and/or vomiting.

